## DESIGN SYSTEM

**Colors (Tailwind: bg-[#hex] or CSS variable):**
- page bg: #0a0b0f | surface (cards): #111318 | surface2: #181b23 | border: #1e2230 | border2: #252a38
- accent (blue): #4f6ef7 | green: #10b981 | orange: #f59e0b | red: #ef4444 | cyan: #06b6d4 | purple: #7c3aed
- text: #e8eaf0 | text2: #8892a4 | text3: #4a5568

**Typography:** Headings -> Syne, sans-serif, weight 700+ | Body -> DM Sans, sans-serif, weight 400-500

**Icons — MANDATORY:** Use lucide-react (preferred) or inline SVG. **Banned:** emojis in any interface element (buttons, sidebar, badges, cards, tables); react-icons without prior approval.
- Correct: `import { Settings, Users, Star, MapPin } from 'lucide-react'` and `<Settings className="w-4 h-4 text-[#8892a4]" />`
- Wrong: emojis in the UI

**Components (reuse — do not recreate):** components/ui/modal.tsx (open?: boolean backward-compatible), toggle.tsx, badge.tsx (green/orange/red/blue/gray), confirm-dialog.tsx. Plan chips: starter=cyan, pro=#4f6ef7, enterprise=#7c3aed. Active nav: bg rgba(79,110,247,0.12) + color #4f6ef7 + 3px left border.

