## DATABASE

**Standards:** IDs and FKs: String(32), uuid.uuid4().hex (no hyphens). Timestamps: DateTime(timezone=True), server_default=func.now(). Never modify migrations 001-017.

**Existing migrations (001-017):** 001-013: users, tenants, user_tenants, plans, niches, modules, plan_niche_modules, blog_posts, site_pages, property_items, leads, schedule_items, media_items, catalog_audit_logs, workspace_externals, integration_apps. 014: tenants ALTER. 015: briefings. 016: tenant_integrations. 017: provisioning_logs.

**Upcoming:** 018 review_items | 019 team_members | 020 faq_categories + faq_items | 021 menu_categories + menu_items | 022 locations | 023 newsletter_subscribers | 024 stripe_products.

