## LEARNED PATTERNS

**Already implemented:** /platform/briefings + /platform/provision/[briefingId], platform sidebar with pending-count badge, api-client.ts Briefing/Provision types, Modal open?: boolean backward-compatible, i18n nav.briefings en/pt/es.

**Mistakes to never repeat:** Ending with "next step" suggestions; hardcoded text without i18n in all 3 files; required prop on shared component; delivery without full pipeline; not confirming container Up; not reading container logs after restart/deploy; emojis in UI or in pipeline reports (use [OK]/[FAIL]); starting a new task without reviewing last implementation.

**What works:** waas-panel.html design system with exact colors; plan chips cyan/blue/purple; pulsing badge for in-progress; pipeline lint->test->build->container->e2e in sequence; immediate log read after every container restart; lucide-react for all interface icons; last-implementation review to catch regressions.
